title: Igor Ledochowski - Covert Trances Hypnosis
description:
I dont think there is anything new in this program that Igor hasnt covered, I cant even tell if its something that hasnt been released here before under another name. If its a dupe I guess Ill find out soon enough. I couldnt find any blurbs for this.

Contents:
CD 01 - Introduction
CD 02 - Rapport and Calibration
CD 03 - Revivification
CD 04 - Tonality
CD 05 - Hypnotic Language
CD 06 - Pacing and Leading
CD 07 - Conscious & Unconscious Disassociation
CD 08 - Metaphor
CD 09 - Embedded Commands
CD 10 - Personal Power
CD 11 - Anchoring
CD 12 - Putting it all together
